    "However, those sensors extract data the analysis and the interpretation of which is complex and hardly straightforward.",
    "Such data will be systematically processed and better understood in the future.",
    "Likewise, EEG wearable biosensors are expected to become more accessible, affordable, and less cumbersome for users to wear.",
